坎波巴索[[海拔|海拔]]{{convert|701|m|ft}}，並非常接近[[亚平宁山脉|亚平宁山脉]]。坎波巴索亦是南意大利其中一個最寒冷的城鎮。坎波巴索的气候類型為[[海洋性气候|海洋性气候]]<ref name=Peel>{{cite journal | author=Peel, M. C. and Finlayson, B. L. and McMahon, T. A. | year=2007 | title=Updated world map of the Köppen–Geiger climate classification | journal=Hydrol. Earth Syst. Sci. | volume=11 | pages=1633–1644 | doi=10.5194/hess-11-1633-2007 | url=http://www.hydrol-earth-syst-sci.net/11/1633/2007/hess-11-1633-2007.html | issn=1027-5606 | access-date=2012-11-29 | archive-date=2017-02-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170210144308/http://www.hydrol-earth-syst-sci.net/11/1633/2007/hess-11-1633-2007.html | dead-url=no }} ''(direct: [http://www.hydrol-earth-syst-sci.net/11/1633/2007/hess-11-1633-2007.pdf Final Revised Paper] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hydrol-earth-syst-sci.net/11/1633/2007/hess-11-1633-2007.pdf |date=20120203170339 }})''</ref>，平均溫度為{{convert|12|°C|F}}，而溫度范围則為{{convert|2|-|22|C|F}}。在冬季，坎波巴索經常下雪。而最潮濕的月份則是11月，月平均降雨量約為{{convert|81|mm|in}}。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.climate-charts.com/Locations/i/IY16252.php |title=坎波巴索氣候 |access-date=2012-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120608001456/http://www.climate-charts.com/Locations/i/IY16252.php |archive-date=2012-06-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

==主要景点==
坎波巴索的主要景点為於1450年由統治者尼古拉二世蒙福特建造的蒙福特城堡。蒙福特城堡是建造於伦巴第人和诺曼人的城堡遺跡上。而主教座堂圣三一堂（Chiesa della Santissima Trinità）則是於1504年建造在城牆外。主教座堂於1805年被一次地震破壞，並於1829年重建。另一個教堂桑巴特鲁姆教堂則是一座建於11世紀的罗马式建築。<ref name="Campobasso"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.molise.worldweb.com/ProvinceofCampobasso/CampobassoCB/SightsAttractions/ |title=坎波巴索主要景点 |accessdate=2012-11-29 |archive-date=2014-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140924171215/http://www.molise.worldweb.com/ProvinceofCampobasso/CampobassoCB/SightsAttractions/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==運輸==
===鐵路===
位於城市中心的坎波巴索火车站建立於1883年，是兩條路線（泰尔莫利到华拉诺路線和贝内文托路線）的交點。<ref>[http://en.structurae.de/structures/data/index.cfm?id=s0039899 坎波巴索火车站]</ref>而坎波巴索亦有火車直通[[羅馬|羅馬]]、[[那不勒斯|那不勒斯]]和[[佩斯卡拉|佩斯卡拉]]。<ref name="trenidicarta.it">{{cite web| author=Alessandro Tuzza and others| url=http://www.trenidicarta.it/aperture.html| title=Prospetto cronologico dei tratti di ferrovia aperti all'esercizio dal 1839 al 31 dicembre 1926| trans_title=Chronological overview of the features of the railways opened between 1839 and 31 December 1926| work=[http://www.trenidicarta.it Trenidicarta.it]| publisher=Alessandro Tuzza| accessdate=26 December 2010| archive-date=2009-06-24| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090624234931/http://www.trenidicarta.it/aperture.html| dead-url=yes}} {{it icon}}</ref>

===道路和公路===
通往坎波巴索的道路有国道SS645、国道647和聖維克多公路。而近年才完工的聖維克多公路令由坎波巴索到羅馬所需的時間大大減少。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://theroyalcanadianregiment.ca/history/1939-1945/campobasso_galloway.html |title=通往坎波巴索的路 |access-date=2012-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111211212905/http://theroyalcanadianregiment.ca/history/1939-1945/campobasso_galloway.html |archive-date=2011-12-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

===公共交通===
城市公共交通總共有23條巴士路線，全部由SEAC公司營運。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ibus.it/english/timetable_coach.asp?idProvIt=campobasso |title=SEAC巴士 |accessdate=2012-11-29 |archive-date=2013-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130123231449/http://ibus.it/english/timetable_coach.asp?idProvIt=campobasso |dead-url=no }}</ref>

